Package org.neo4j.kernel.impl.store

Class NeoStores

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.kernel.impl.store.NeoStores
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    public class NeoStores
extends Object
implements AutoCloseable
    This class contains the references to the "NodeStore,RelationshipStore, PropertyStore and RelationshipTypeStore". NeoStores doesn't actually "store" anything but extends the AbstractStore for the "type and version" validation performed in there.
